#: ../../language/error_codes/E4208.md:1
msgid "E4208"
msgstr "E4208"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4208.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `unknown_regex_match_binding`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`unknown_regex_match_binding`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4208.md:5
msgid "Unknown regex match binding."
msgstr "未知的正则匹配绑定。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4208.md:7
msgid ""
"Regex match expressions support only the special bindings `before` and "
"`after` beside the matched regex itself. `before` binds the unmatched "
"prefix and `after` binds the unmatched suffix."
msgstr ""
"正则匹配表达式除匹配的正则本身外，只支持特殊绑定 `before` 和 `after`。"
"`before` 绑定未匹配的前缀，`after` 绑定未匹配的后缀。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4208.md:11
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4208.md:13
msgid ""
"fn match_text(s : String) -> Unit {\n"
"  ignore(s =~ (re\"a\", middle=mid))\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4208.md:17
msgid "`middle` is not a supported regex match binding label."
msgstr "`middle` 不是受支持的正则匹配绑定标签。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4208.md:19
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4208.md:21
msgid "Use `before` or `after`, or bind the regex itself with `as`."
msgstr "使用 `before` 或 `after`，或者用 `as` 绑定正则本身。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4208.md:23
msgid ""
"fn match_text(s : String) -> Unit {\n"
"  ignore(s =~ (re\"a\", before=head))\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
